{@--1@} A particle having an
interrogative force and implying
some ‘doubt’, or ‘uncertainty’;
{#svapno nu mAyA nu matiBramo nu#} <ls>Ś. 6. 9</ls>;
{#astaSElagahanaM nu vivasvAnAviveSa jalaDiM#}
{#nu mahIM nu#} <ls>Ki. 9. 7</ls>; <ls n="Ki.">5. 1</ls>; <ls n="Ki.">8. 53</ls>,
<ls n="Ki.">9. 15</ls>, <ls n="Ki. 9.">54</ls>; <ls n="Ki.">13. 4</ls>; <ls>Ku. 1. 46</ls>;  
<ls>Śi. 10. 14</ls>; <ls>Ś. 2. 9.</ls>

{@--2@} It is very often 
compounded with the interrogative 
pronoun and its derivatives in the sense
of ‘possibly’, ‘indeed’; {#kiM#} 
{#nvetatsyAtkimanyadito'TavA#} <ls>Māl. 1. 17</ls>; {#kaTaMnu#} 

{#guRavadviMdeyaM kalatraM#} Dk; see {#kiMnu#} also.
